      "raw_text": "WENATCHEE Wash, oct. 90\nThe okanogan Irrigation and I'm\nprovement company is planning an\nirrigation project in the northt CEN\ntrail part of Okanogan county,\nwhich will entail the expenditure\nOf 100000 and will put 1900\nacres of land under water. The\nproject will be one of the largest\nin the northwest. Colonel A. M.\nDewey Of Spokane reports that he\nhas succeeded in floating the bonds\nin the east and work will be started\nin November."
